rpc.dataretrieval
Class NopAggregator

java.lang.Object
  rpc.dataretrieval.Aggregator
      rpc.dataretrieval.NopAggregator

public class NopAggregator
extends Aggregator

Extension of the abstract aggregator that uses no operator. A NopAggregator must be the base aggregator for all other aggregator objects.
